{"bbox": [6, 22, 986, 212], "block_id": "block-0000", "block_index": 0, "chunk_id": "chk-9de40f9f30bb3ca5", "chunk_type": "text", "dataset": "workspace_867d147ce35b", "document_id": "doc-1376aba4c3df7fb8", "image_path": "D:\\MLLMProject\\data\\workspaces\\867d147ce35b\\raw\\711e0f1081_理论作业1.jpg", "metadata": {"block_index": 0, "parser": "mineru", "raw_index": 0, "raw_type": "text"}, "page_no": 1, "part_index": 0, "sample_id": "711e0f1081", "source_path": "D:\\MLLMProject\\data\\workspaces\\867d147ce35b\\raw\\711e0f1081_理论作业1.jpg", "source_ref": "workspace_867d147ce35b/workspace/711e0f1081#page=1#block=block-0000", "split": "workspace", "text": "对于一个拥有n个样本和m个特征的训练数据集，我们使用线性回归模型进行拟合。样本的特征矩阵为X（一个n×（m＋1)矩阵，已包含偏置项），对应的真实值标签为向量y（一个n×1向量）。模型的参数为向量w（一个(m+1)×1向量）。"}
