{"bbox": [52, 574, 982, 692], "block_id": "block-0005", "block_index": 5, "chunk_id": "chk-e83d887fd3e813d8", "chunk_type": "text", "dataset": "workspace_867d147ce35b", "document_id": "doc-1376aba4c3df7fb8", "image_path": "D:\\MLLMProject\\data\\workspaces\\867d147ce35b\\raw\\711e0f1081_理论作业1.jpg", "metadata": {"block_index": 5, "parser": "mineru", "raw_index": 5, "raw_type": "text"}, "page_no": 1, "part_index": 0, "sample_id": "711e0f1081", "source_path": "D:\\MLLMProject\\data\\workspaces\\867d147ce35b\\raw\\711e0f1081_理论作业1.jpg", "source_ref": "workspace_867d147ce35b/workspace/711e0f1081#page=1#block=block-0005", "split": "workspace", "text": "当代价函数L(w)是凸函数时，其最优解 $\\pmb { w } ^ { * }$ 可以通过令其梯度为零找到。请写出该最优解的矩阵形式表达式（也称为正规方程解）。"}
{"bbox": [21, 730, 367, 775], "block_id": "block-0006", "block_index": 6, "chunk_id": "chk-d0cd70de5a44f48a", "chunk_type": "text", "dataset": "workspace_867d147ce35b", "document_id": "doc-1376aba4c3df7fb8", "image_path": "D:\\MLLMProject\\data\\workspaces\\867d147ce35b\\raw\\711e0f1081_理论作业1.jpg", "metadata": {"block_index": 6, "parser": "mineru", "raw_index": 6, "raw_type": "text"}, "page_no": 1, "part_index": 0, "sample_id": "711e0f1081", "source_path": "D:\\MLLMProject\\data\\workspaces\\867d147ce35b\\raw\\711e0f1081_理论作业1.jpg", "source_ref": "workspace_867d147ce35b/workspace/711e0f1081#page=1#block=block-0006", "split": "workspace", "text": "3．梯度下降(Gradient Descent)"}
